Package: growd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: P2P digital currency - daemon
 grow is a free open source peer-to-peer electronic currency system that
 is completely decentralized, without the need for a central server or
 trusted parties.  Users hold the private keys for their own coins and
 transact directly with each other, with the help of a P2P network to
 check for double-spending.
 .
 By default connects to an IRC network to discover other peers.
 .
 Full transaction history is stored locally at each client. The size of
 this file grows over time.
 .
 This package provides growd, a combined daemon and CLI tool to
 interact with the daemon.

Package: grow-qt
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: P2P network based digital currency - Qt GUI
 Coypasta is a free open source peer-to-peer electronic currency that
 is completely decentralized, without the need for a central server or
 trusted parties.  Users hold the keys to their own coins and
 transact directly with each other, with the help of a P2P network to
 check for double-spending.
 .
 By default connects to an IRC network to discover other peers.
 .
 Full transaction history is stored locally at each client.  The size of
 this file grows over time.
 .
 This package provides grow-Qt, a GUI for grow based on Qt.
